reviewText:
Third season was a bit creepier and even more unrealistic, what with the body in the gatehouse in suspended animation.
Still, interesting.
all house of anubis episodes are great
My granddaughter and I really enjoyed this third season of the series and we would recommend it for other fans.
I like a good clean family friendly mystery series. Can't wait for season 4 to come out. Thanks for putt.ing this on DVD
Pre-ordered this DVD and it was here sooner than I thought. My son loves this show and we don't get it with our cable. Thanks again!
Item as described.
Fantastic

The entire series is awesome. Great mysteries for 9-14 year olds.  Fun for parents, too. No sex, no swearing, no smoking...and the kids are so busy they don't have all that much time to be stuck in front of screens.  We've watched it 3 times from start to finish, and will likely continue to do so over and over throughout the years.

My package arrived damaged.

Initially the back of the package says "Full Screen" so I was a little worried. However, the worries went away as IT IS actually Widescreen. The quality is amazing as well, almost HD like. Same goes for volume 1.

Great show, well put together, with characters that are well developed, and you either like and root for, or love to hate.  An unexpected hit that could have gone on longer.  Full of suspense, intrigue, and mystery.  The whole series is good.
They can make an awesome series even without the main character. But yeah, House of Anubis is not the same without Nina and Amber
thank you
waited a long time to get in our r1 region

I bought this whole series for my niece.  I gave her a couple for Christmas, A couple for birthday and then another special occasion completed the set.  She was excited!  She had got into the series when she started watching them on You Tube.  She was happy that she was able to see them on her tv and finally had closure.  My niece is 13 now and she is very happy with this and the rest of the set!  I would probably even watch these myself!  As far as a review of the actual show, it all depends upon your own taste.
